          SYSTEM:   Darwin Information Typing Architecture (DITA)

          PURPOSE:  Adds Reveal Data Attribute Domain for reveal.js data-* attributes related to
                    auto-animation and codeblocks. See https://revealjs.com/auto-animate/ and https://revealjs.com/code/.
                    
                    data-background-* attributes are not included; to use, add as prolog/data where @name 
                    is the name of the data-background-* attribute and the value is in the element's text()  

